    Represents health status of battery in scanner accessory

    Represents state of bonding/pairing establishment w.r.t remote device

    Represents state of connection establishment w.r.t remote device

    Represents reason for remote device disconnection

    Represents categories of error that might occur during run time of BT analyzer.
    BtInsightConstants.EventType
    Represents events types of all features in BT analyzer
    BtInsightConstants.Feature
    Represents different features that can be supported by BT analyzer

    BtInsightConstants.PeripheralType
    Represents peripheral(remote) device type.
    BtInsightConstants.ProfileType
